Note that the completeness assumption is necessary. Let `E` be the space `‚Ñï ‚Üí‚ÇÄ ‚Ñù` with inner space
structure inherited from `PiLp 2 (fun _ : ‚Ñï ‚Ü¶ ‚Ñù)`. Let `K` be the subspace of sequences with the sum
